title: Danny & Audrina Patridge (The Hills)

description:
Danny chats with Audrina Patridge, formerly of The Hills on MTV, about the original series, what happened with the reboot, her new book (Choices, avail now), opening up about her relationships, dating Chris Pine, and so much more!
